AUDIO: 'living in the dark ages of Slop Overflow. Instead of grinding for hours and earning those sweet dopamine hits line by line, you now just tell the AI what you want and watch it hallucinate an entire code base. Writing code isn\'t fun anymore, layoffs are intensifying,'

